Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.76,0:00:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牧瀨…紅莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.23,0:00:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好歹算是敲過門了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.54,0:00:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.43,0:00:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從橋田同學那裡問來的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.36,0:00:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為說是實驗室
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.29,0:00:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為是更像樣的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.48,0:00:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桶子 你難道背叛了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.67,0:00:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被這個三次元的女人色誘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋 不可原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.25,0:00:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法原諒！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.48,0:00:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個Bitch！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.09,0:00:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橋田同學你能管管他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.21,0:00:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這在這種情況下就當作他已經陷入混亂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.03,0:00:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊急事態 機關終於派間諜潛入這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.40,0:00:41.76,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(693,630)}Steins Gate
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.40,0:00:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？ 這也是命運石之門的選擇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.00,0:00:43.48,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(617,630)}Steins Gate
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.00,0:00:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運石之門？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.48,0:00:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡倫的腦內設定而已 沒啥特別的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來也是 德語和英語混在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.41,0:00:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把鞋子脫了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.60,0:00:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 因為我一直待在美國
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.23,0:01:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新打一下招呼吧 我是牧瀨紅莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.24,0:01:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,握手都不會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.10,0:01:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本的男人是不是太缺乏常識了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.41,0:01:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.21,0:01:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身上散發出的殺氣非比尋常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.84,0:01:23.84,neta1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(15,20,15,10,0,200)\pos(15,10)\fad(300,300)}Martial Arts
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.54,0:01:24.04,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx0\pos(15,20)\t(0,200,1,\fscx115)\t(5300,0,1,\fscx0)}———
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.84,0:01:23.84,neta3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(15,20,15,50,0,200)\pos(15,50)\fad(300,300)}中文「武術」的英譯，而在日語裡是格鬥技的總稱。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.04,0:01:21.76,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(779,630)}Martial Arts
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.04,0:01:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是俗話所說的武術嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.68,0:01:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.90,0:01:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說確實看見我被刺殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.15,0:01:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是事實 還是你用來性騷擾的藉口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.39,0:01:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想來做個確認而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.29,0:01:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.95,0:03:12.96,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(779,652)}並列過程的偏執狂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.55,0:03:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結合部沒有損傷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來沒有機關
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.80,0:03:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她搞不好會設置爆炸物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.39,0:03:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別放鬆監視
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.14,0:03:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.68,0:03:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有鑷子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.35,0:03:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.93,0:03:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.81,0:03:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面黏糊糊的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.69,0:03:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.48,0:03:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.52,0:03:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真難吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.27,0:03:43.44,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(683,630)}The Zombie
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.27,0:03:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這「復蘇者」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.44,0:03:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了的話就直說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.44,0:03:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香蕉的話還是能賞一根給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.11,0:03:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰要吃變態的香蕉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然說我變態？！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然黏上來 還摸來摸去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.91,0:03:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牧瀨氏 牧瀨氏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:04:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「誰要吃變態的香蕉啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.96,0:04:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能麻煩你再說一遍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.71,0:04:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話 儘量擺出一副懊悔的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.71,0:04:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懊悔的表情？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.80,0:04:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼臉紅了 難道在想像些什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.72,0:04:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說說看吧 天才少女
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.43,0:04:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天才到底在想像些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.09,0:04:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能說明一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.26,0:04:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你們兩個都是變態呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.85,0:04:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.85,0:04:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒在誇你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.73,0:04:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如說 做了變態想像的一方才是變態吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.98,0:04:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變態天才少女
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.94,0:04:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰是變態啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.77,0:04:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 說實話本來都到了可以馬上控告你性騷擾的程度了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.24,0:04:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過現在我暫且不追究
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.78,0:04:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.70,0:04:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以告訴我詳細情況
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.86,0:04:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個香蕉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.66,0:04:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那個烤箱有什麼關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.37,0:04:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是最高機密
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來電子機械8號機
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.37,0:04:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電話烤箱（暫定）可是我們研究所的秘密武器啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.17,0:04:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 牧瀨氏的話搞不好能解開這個奇異機能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.94,0:04:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.88,0:05:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如說 僅憑我們的話絕對不可能搞清楚啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.81,0:05:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 說到底這可是我們未來電子機械研究所的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.65,0:05:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說了自己叫克莉絲蒂娜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.50,0:05:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽我哪張嘴這麼說了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想知道這個電話烤箱（暫定）秘密是有條件的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.09,0:05:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.51,0:05:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必須成為這個未來電子機械研究所的Labmem
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.31,0:05:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說成為這個研究所的成員嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.60,0:05:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我預定8月中旬就回美國了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那之前就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.11,0:05:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 另外一個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.28,0:05:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後不再追究任何我對你進行性騷擾的行為
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.41,0:05:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這些
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.53,0:05:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡倫你好小器 作為一個「人」的器量太小了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:52.21,neta1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(15,20,15,10,0,200)\pos(15,10)\fad(300,300)}崇拜得渾身酥軟 / そこに痺れる憧れる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.91,0:05:52.41,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx0\pos(15,20)\t(0,200,1,\fscx338)\t(5300,0,1,\fscx0)}———
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:52.21,neta3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(15,20,15,50,0,200)\pos(15,50)\fad(300,300)}用來表現對能做出超常行為的人或事的敬仰和吃驚之情。\N也用於諷刺。出處是《JOJO的奇妙冒險》第一部。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.41,0:05:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的這一點我是崇拜得渾身酥軟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.04,0:05:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.16,0:05:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 這個條件還不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.00,0:05:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你來說而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.46,0:06:00.46,neta1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(15,20,15,10,0,200)\pos(15,10)\fad(300,300)}去甲腎上腺素
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.12,0:06:00.63,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx0\pos(15,20)\t(0,200,1,\fscx120)\t(5300,0,1,\fscx0)}———
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.46,0:06:00.46,neta3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(15,20,15,50,0,200)\pos(15,50)\fad(300,300)}腦內分泌的一種神經傳遞物質。\N正確的叫法是「norepinephrine」。\N當人類感到憤怒的時候就會分泌這種物質。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.63,0:05:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 感覺去甲腎上腺素都分泌過度了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.13,0:06:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 你要怎麼辦 克莉絲蒂娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.26,0:06:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說了 不要加蒂娜兩個字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.09,0:06:05.09,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(737,630)}The Zombie
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.09,0:06:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,條件不錯吧 「復蘇者」喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了好好叫我名字！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳳凰院變態凶真
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰變態啊 天才變態少女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.18,0:06:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變態之間的視線戰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.97,0:06:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃起來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.52,0:06:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴 變態
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.85,0:06:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我接受條件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 不准再叫我變態了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.11,0:06:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不會再當你是變態了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.19,0:06:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 那麼從現在開始你就是Labmem NO.004
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.36,0:06:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克莉絲～蒂娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.53,0:06:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不准加蒂娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.07,0:06:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燴飯～炸雞～No.1 one！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.83,0:06:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:37.66,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是瞬間移動嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由結果出發的思考是很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.92,0:06:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那妳說是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用香蕉串或冷凍炸雞的時候並沒有瞬間移動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:47.17,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一…二…三…四…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.17,0:06:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 有客人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了 我是牧瀨紅莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.76,0:06:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就來拜訪 真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:06:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是椎名真由理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.93,0:07:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像我也成為了Labmem…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Labmem？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.64,0:07:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.56,0:07:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子的…Labmem啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.90,0:07:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼稀奇嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.44,0:07:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是除了真由喜以外的第一個女性Labmem
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.15,0:07:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.41,0:07:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.99,0:07:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.28,0:07:20.16,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.74,0:07:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像發生了放電現象
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼剛剛不說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.33,0:07:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴我具體情況
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.04,0:07:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.46,0:07:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是從烤箱出現了類似閃電一樣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.17,0:07:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼時候的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.17,0:07:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是昨天中午吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.72,0:07:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡倫看到人工衛星墜落的新聞跑出去後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.89,0:07:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把自己的手機和這東西接在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…我發那封郵件的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.23,0:07:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的手機和電話烤箱（暫定）是接在一起的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.94,0:07:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那則說牧瀨氏被刺殺了的郵件？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.94,0:07:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是一周前發的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.61,0:08:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 那是昨天中午…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.11,0:08:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡 在哪裡 為什麼沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.78,0:08:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放電現象發生時 烤箱的情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.37,0:08:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為在做功能測試 所以正在使用逆回轉機能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.25,0:08:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來還是再現一下當時的情況比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.46,0:08:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理 把燴飯炸雞No.1拿到這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.50,0:08:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.59,0:08:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 大家也要吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.13,0:08:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一人一個的話 可以給你們哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.13,0:08:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有必要整盒放進去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.51,0:08:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逆回轉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.68,0:08:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想觀察一下裡面東西的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.39,0:08:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桶子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.18,0:08:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,助手 發郵件到我的手機
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.81,0:08:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼時候變成你的助手了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.27,0:08:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說了 我又不知道你的郵件地址
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.86,0:08:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是派不上用場的助手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.52,0:08:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桶子 用你的手機吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.61,0:08:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內容呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.74,0:08:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.11,0:08:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就發「克莉絲蒂娜是變態」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.91,0:08:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說了禁止說變態嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.91,0:08:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我就折衷 發「岡倫是變態」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.74,0:08:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橋田同學 GJ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.58,0:08:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我發送了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.67,0:09:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就等手機收信了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.96,0:09:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.96,0:09:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.97,0:09:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.35,0:09:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換氣 換氣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.40,0:09:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.19,0:09:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電磁波的力量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.11,0:09:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說傻話了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.78,0:09:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微波爐的電磁波不可能這麼短的時間內劈開桌子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.53,0:09:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 烤焦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.79,0:09:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易買回來的說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.25,0:09:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地板上的洞怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.83,0:09:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被顯像管氏發現的話 我們可不會有好結果啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.76,0:09:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.67,0:09:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:10:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收信日期 7月24日 17點30分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實送到過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.48,0:10:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白些什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.85,0:10:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 一切都聯繫在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看見了 能解釋一系列事件的唯一答案
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.94,0:10:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.98,0:10:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從香蕉串上切下來的香蕉回到了串上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.19,0:10:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郵件被送到了5天前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.74,0:10:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事…難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.91,0:10:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是這個難道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.28,0:10:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個電話烤爐（暫定）是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.83,0:10:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間機器啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郵件13封？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.10,0:10:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃光的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.60,0:10:56.40,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(822,630)}Shining Finger
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.60,0:10:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我確實取名叫她閃光的指壓師了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.56,0:10:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這個數量真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.53,0:11:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請立刻回覆郵件給我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.07,0:11:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道在睡覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.82,0:11:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想睡到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.24,0:11:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桶子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去散個步吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.33,0:11:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.25,0:11:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擊太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熬夜居然毫無結果什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.50,0:11:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在後悔自己做這種傻事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.88,0:11:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼變不了膠蕉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.01,0:11:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.43,0:11:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郵件也只成功發送了那一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.39,0:11:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是把牧瀨氏叫回來比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.35,0:11:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不擺明不可能嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.52,0:11:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.27,0:11:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能是時間機器…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.94,0:11:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說著這話就跑出去了沒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.16,0:11:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底出什麼事了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.08,0:11:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.33,0:11:53.33,neta1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(15,20,15,10,0,200)\pos(15,10)\fad(300,300)}LHC
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.99,0:11:53.50,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx0\pos(15,20)\t(0,200,1,\fscx40)\t(5300,0,1,\fscx0)}———
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.33,0:11:53.33,neta3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(15,20,15,50,0,200)\pos(15,50)\fad(300,300)}Large Hadron Collider，大型強子對撞器。將各種帶電粒子加速，\N並讓它們發生衝撞進而研究衝撞後發生的反應的實驗裝置。\N比較主要的幾個對撞機除了SERN的LHC之外，\N其餘分佈於美國和英國，包括日本也在內。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.49,0:11:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LHC
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.70,0:11:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.58,0:11:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大型強子對撞機 SERN的基本粒子加速器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.79,0:11:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是治癒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.13,0:12:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間機器被SERN獨占了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.18,0:12:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約翰‧提托
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.52,0:12:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前說過的那傢伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.44,0:12:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在@ch上就跟祭典一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.15,0:12:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SERN是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.98,0:12:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提托說的 SERN在2034年完成了時間機器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.95,0:12:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意義不明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.45,0:12:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管了 告訴我 SERN到底是…
