Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡通知？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.33,0:15:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 玩笑啦玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.71,0:15:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個對IBN5100這夢幻PC無比熱心的女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.88,0:15:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IBN？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.09,0:15:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎
