Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是在網路上看見的
