Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.45,0:18:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你們已經連續兩天熬夜了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.88,0:18:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以買了慰問品來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.59,0:18:53.59,neta1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(15,20,15,10,0,200)\pos(15,10)\fad(300,300)}罐裝關東煮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.59,0:18:53.59,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx0\pos(15,20)\t(0,200,1,\fscx100)\t(5300,0,1,\fscx0)}———
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.59,0:18:53.59,neta3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(15,20,15,50,0,200)\pos(15,50)\fad(300,300)}在罐裝果汁一樣的容器中加入多種食材的雜燴而製成的東西。\N自1990年初這種罐頭開始入駐秋葉原的配件商店店前的自動販賣機，\N在那之後人氣漸漸上升，現在已經成為秋葉原的名產品之一。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.79,0:18:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罐裝關東煮嗎 感激不盡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.13,0:18:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後也拜託了 真由理
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.96,0:18:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由喜的零用錢還沒有多到能夠老是請客啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.05,0:19:03.06,neta1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(15,20,15,10,0,200)\pos(15,10)\fad(300,300)}雷Net
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.76,0:19:03.22,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx0\pos(15,20)\t(0,200,1,\fscx58)\t(5300,0,1,\fscx0)}———
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.05,0:19:03.06,neta3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(15,20,15,50,0,200)\pos(15,50)\fad(300,300)}（架空）洛克洛克漫畫連載中的、以網路為主題的超人氣漫畫。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.26,0:19:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還要買雷Net的香腸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.56,0:19:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是烏帕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.97,0:19:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說要認真品嘗味道才行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.27,0:19:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有桶子君和克莉絲醬的份哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.06,0:19:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了不是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.07,0:19:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒在聽…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.90,0:19:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也說過要他去休息一會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.86,0:19:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級廚客的魂正在熊熊燃燒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.49,0:19:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少叫我廚客！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.37,0:19:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 偷看是不好的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.71,0:19:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了揭露SERN的陰謀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.17,0:19:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.88,0:19:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克莉絲醬肯定也是因為生氣了 才一下子衝出去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.93,0:19:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那個跟入侵沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.55,0:19:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是助手自作主張而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.39,0:19:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會再來呢 克莉絲醬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.02,0:19:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.86,0:19:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用炸魚餅換牛筋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.03,0:19:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？ 那我想換鵪鶉蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.65,0:19:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.57,0:20:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了牛筋 我第二喜歡的就是鵪鶉蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.62,0:20:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由喜也喜歡鵪鶉蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.95,0:20:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就用竹輪將就一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.87,0:20:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 炸魚餅還不如竹輪呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.75,0:20:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 交涉成立
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.71,0:20:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真由喜的牛筋…咦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.50,0:20:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.50,0:20:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 什麼時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.92,0:20:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相當美味
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.60,0:20:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.97,0:20:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了 來了 來了 來了 來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.10,0:20:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.39,0:20:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖地把一切都展現在我眼前吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.19,0:20:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了！ ID入手！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.84,0:20:34.81,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.05,0:20:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務完成！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.33,0:20:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊 雖然不太懂是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過就算入侵了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.65,0:20:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是管理者ID的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.47,0:20:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瀏覽範圍也是相當有限的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.68,0:20:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺就和只能看到胸部一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.10,0:20:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桶子君真H呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內容呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.10,0:20:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在只是找到了幾封郵件而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.52,0:20:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英文嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.31,0:21:01.32,neta1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(15,20,15,10,0,200)\pos(15,10)\fad(300,300)}Excite
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.31,0:21:01.32,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx0\pos(15,20)\t(0,200,1,\fscx58)\t(5300,0,1,\fscx0)}———
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.31,0:21:01.32,neta3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(15,20,15,50,0,200)\pos(15,50)\fad(300,300)}翻譯網站的名稱。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.52,0:20:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻有請Excite老師登場
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.48,0:21:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會做那麼麻煩的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.19,0:21:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翻譯過來就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.57,0:21:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HI 保羅！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.73,0:21:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種演技就免了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.32,0:21:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.53,0:21:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.70,0:21:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LHC狀態不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.36,0:21:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這東西就跟貓一樣任性
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.58,0:21:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這一個月以來 狀態卻好得驚人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.74,0:21:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.20,0:21:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.25,0:21:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個 找不到有關時間機器痕跡的文件嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.08,0:21:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然時間機器這個單詞沒出現過
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.09,0:21:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是「Z Program」這個詞卻在這個月裡被用了上百次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.88,0:21:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.92,0:21:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第137次「Z Program」實驗報告
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.39,0:21:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於製造迷你黑洞的任務已經確立 所以省略了報告
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.19,0:21:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷你黑洞…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.02,0:21:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是啊 明明官方發表說結果是實驗失敗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.73,0:21:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.03,0:21:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實驗結果…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.86,0:22:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Human is Dead. Mismatch
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.53,0:22:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Human is Dead…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.62,0:22:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.08,0:22:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了

